@DATABASE "Qarx"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - Q - Qarx"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - Q
                   ====================================

                                   Qarx
                                   ====



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46064,0)"}         46064,0
@{"Lives = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(44996,255)"}         44996,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Start Level = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(44991,1)"}         44996,x (x= 1-10)
@{"Immunity       " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(45944,0) ZXAMPoke(45945,0)"}         45944,0:45945,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         I think the maximum level is 10. I tried higher
                         numbers than that, and just got a load of crap.

                         Rastan
@endnode
